svg.text: The Usual Suspects: Where Nobel Laureates Are From
Research facilities and funding tend to be concentrated in a handful of countries, and the winners reflect that imbalance. Over the years, the
winners have come from the same eight countries, but the “rest of the world” has kept pace, especially with the Nobel Peace Prize.
The Usual Suspects: Where Nobel Laureates Are From

text.tspan: Research facilities and funding are concentrated in only a few countries, and the winners tend to come from those countries.
However, the “rest of the world” has kept pace, especially with the Nobel Peace Prize.
